From 274f30e00840cfe0d4476f3b7959cf847a4f9104 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mirco Miranda <mirco.miranda@systemceramics.com>
Date: Fri, 18 Aug 2023 15:11:41 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] qoi: fix buffer overflow kf5

Backport of MR !167:
- fix buffer overflow with corrupted images without image data
- fix unable to read very small images (e.g. 1x1 px)
- new test cases added
- detect incomplete files by checking the end of streams as written in the specs
